  "texts": [
    "Section 3 provides the detailed survey and analysis on the trends, methods, and topics in sentiment analysis of Chinese text, outlining the evolution of methodologies in multilingual sentiment analysis, especially with a focus on the Chinese language.",
    "Section 4 explores the practical applications, limitations, and future prospects of Chinese sentiment analysis.",
    "Lastly, Sect. 5 and Sect.",
    "6 conclude the paper and discuss potential future directions.",
    "Sentiment analysis, a cornerstone of natural language processing, has undergone extensive exploration across a multitude of languages, cultures, and contexts (Abdullah and Rusli 2021; Cui et al. 2023; Mihalcea et al. 2012; Araújo et al. 2020)."
  ]
}